{"tid":1951233,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"隊報:美斯就是巴塞的其古華拉 帶零隊友反抗高層","createTime":"2020-03-31T00:54:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-01T01:34:27.000Z","uid":173952,"like":7,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"02502481ccc50374b67252dbdcc4312f99802707","tid":1951233,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T00:54:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zV6UKNE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzV6UKNE.jpg&h=27033f63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美斯被p成切-古華拉<br />\n<br />\n  昨晚美斯等巴塞一線隊球員集體宣佈，接受降薪70%，不過在公告中，他們表示球會有向他們施壓的行為。<br />\n<br />\n  美斯在公告中表示：「一直讓我們感到驚訝的是，在球會內部有人試圖把我們置於放大鏡下，並試圖施加壓力，讓我們做一些我們知道自己會做的事情。」《馬卡報》就分析說，美斯這話顯然是在直接抨擊巴塞的董事會，指責他們不該在降薪一事上，對球員施加壓力。<br />\n<br />\n隊報封面<br />\n<br />\n  而《隊報》則將美斯放到了最新的封面上，同時還將美斯P成了古巴革命領導人之一的切-古華拉，並打出了「巴塞的切-古華拉&mdash;&mdash;美斯」的大標題。「巴塞球會的王牌在隊友的支持下抨擊了管理層，阿根廷人支持在當前的情況下減薪，但他譴責了高層的行為。」<br />\n<br />\n  切-古華拉是古巴革命的主要領導人之一，並在其他第三世界國家進行了反帝遊擊戰爭。1967年被捕遭殺害之後，他的肖像逐漸成為了反抗的象徵。"},{"pid":"7a259344e5b6f40167b39b0f27465ae4fa7c8df5","tid":1951233,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T00:54:45.000Z","msg":"希望佢堅定d反抗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6c71b83862bf36149293d09f04149ba1d4f8f53","tid":1951233,"uid":43785,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T01:38:32.000Z","msg":"光復巴塞，美斯革命，好熱血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打倒巴塞垃圾管理層，還我歐聯"},{"pid":"4fc7d8066ac6efe95263a814ee014b4a067002fc","tid":1951233,"uid":12628,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T03:00:05.000Z","msg":"張圖成個乞兒咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbd8e881a798799dc3605e5e4e01ae956d141ac7","tid":1951233,"uid":67225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T04:35:12.000Z","msg":"其古華拉???????????????????????????????????"},{"pid":"a370579acade6e290f0b9d3309e60055a4a3f022","tid":1951233,"uid":90515,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T05:47:45.000Z","msg":"President Bartomeu: &quot;When the 70% salary cut was proposed, Messi said 'you have to do this' from the first moment.&quot; [sport]<br />\n<br />\nBartomeu: &quot;The proposal for the extra contribution came from the captains, and it's a gesture that shows their commitment to the club.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n希望各位唔好再笑活蛇，人一天不能受太多刺激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5376d8d6770dc581e41deace090a67e97c0bd24e","tid":1951233,"uid":44285,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T06:29:13.000Z","msg":"收皮啦賤種樓主大陸fake news狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我貼就唔係fake (活著何求，2020)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1950932\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1950932</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"154a46c5ca0ff5b234543f1ca6af7e4a0bab77bc","tid":1951233,"uid":91152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a370579acade6e290f0b9d3309e60055a4a3f022","tid":1951233,"uid":90515,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T05:47:45.000Z","msg":"President Bartomeu: &quot;When the 70% salary cut was proposed, Messi said 'you have to do this' from the first moment.&quot; [sport]<br />\n<br />\nBartomeu: &quot;The proposal for the extra contribution came from the captains, and it's a gesture that shows their commitment to the club.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n希望各位唔好再笑活蛇，人一天不能受太多刺激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T06:33:04.000Z","msg":"lmao"},{"pid":"df478e745f47c1695f17a398ba4c9e6dc672778b","tid":1951233,"uid":35507,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T06:33:13.000Z","msg":"又share支拿news<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p